《'''永不屈服'''》（{{lang-en|Salting the Battlefield}}），2014年英國電視電影，以[[英國安全局|英國安全局]]（軍情五處，MI5）為背景的政治諜報片，導演大衛·海爾「-{zh:約翰尼;zh-cn:钱宁;zh-tw:強尼;}-·沃里克」三部曲中的第三部，場景拉回[[歐洲|歐洲]]。<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/tv/news/a478584/bill-nighy-christopher-walken-for-bbc-twos-page-eight-sequels.html | title=Bill Nighy, Christopher Walken for BBC Two's 'Page Eight' sequels | work=Digital Spy | date=3 May 2013 | accessdate=16 February 2014 | author=Jeffery, Morgan | language=en | archive-date=2015-09-24 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924222201/http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/tv/news/a478584/bill-nighy-christopher-walken-for-bbc-twos-page-eight-sequels.html | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/coming-soon-in-2014-a-look-at-the-year-ahead-in-arts-9027419.html | title=Coming soon in 2014: A look at the year ahead in arts | work=The Independent | date=29 December 2013 | accessdate=16 February 2014 | author=Williams, Holly; Finamore, Emma | language=en | archive-date=2015-09-24 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924150021/http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/coming-soon-in-2014-a-look-at-the-year-ahead-in-arts-9027419.html | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.express.co.uk/entertainment/tv-radio/459513/From-heart-tugging-wartime-sagas-to-gritty-cop-shows-10-dramas-you-must-see-this-spring | title=From heart-tugging wartime sagas to gritty cop shows: 10 dramas you must see this spring | work=Daily Express | date=15 February 2014 | accessdate=16 February 2014 | author=Power, Vicki | language=en | archive-date=2015-07-21 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150721201015/http://www.express.co.uk/entertainment/tv-radio/459513/From-heart-tugging-wartime-sagas-to-gritty-cop-shows-10-dramas-you-must-see-this-spring | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-26187878 | title=Carey Mulligan and Bill Nighy to play ex-lovers in